<div class="NavHead" style="font-size: 105%; background: transparent; text-align: left; color:white; background-color:#9e003a; text-align:center; Padding:2px 1px 2px 1px; line-height= 1;;"><a href="Mu'tazila" title="Mu'tazila"><span style="color:white;">Mu'tazila</span></a></div>
<div class="NavContent" style="font-size: 105%; padding: 0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align: center;"><b><a href="Comments_on_the_Peak_of_Eloquence_(book_by_Abd_al-Hamid)" title="Comments on the Peak of Eloquence (book by Abd al-Hamid)" class="mw-redirect"><span style="color:#9e003a;">Comments on the Peak of Eloquence</span></a></b> <i><span style="font-size:85%;">(?–1258)</span></i>
